description:
&lt;p&gt;University College London Hospital are seeking Band 6 junior pharmacists to join the Staff Bank.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Essential Requirements;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Right to work in the UK&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A minimum of 6 months experience working within the NHS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work under pressure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to communicate accurately and effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job purpose;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Being responsible pharmacist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Screening and dispensing hospital and private prescriptions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serving OTC complimentary medicines and advice giving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Training will be given on the job.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in this role please apply online today and attach your CV&lt;/p&gt;
